'''Ştefan Stoica''' (1976 – 4 February 2014) was a [[Romania]]n politician. He was a member of the [[Senate (Romania)|Senate]] from 2012 to 2014.
A [[physician]] by profession, he was a member of the [[Democratic Liberal Party (Romania)|Democratic Liberal Party]] before switching to the [[People's Party – Dan Diaconescu]], and he was [[Romanian legislative election, 2012|elected]] while belonging to that party, for a seat in [[Ialomița County]]. In October 2013, he defected to the [[Social Democratic Party (Romania)|Social Democratic Party]].<ref>{{ro icon}} Eliana Rădulescu, [http://www.mediafax.ro/politic/senatorul-stefan-stoica-in-varsta-de-37-de-ani-a-murit-12018156 "Senatorul Ştefan Stoica, în vârstă de 37 de ani, a merit"], Mediafax, February 4, 2014</ref><ref>{{ro icon}} [http://www.cdep.ro/pls/parlam/structura.mp?idm=151&cam=1&leg=2012 Parliamentary profile] at the Chamber of Deputies site</ref>
Stoica died of cancer at the age of 37.<ref>[http://www.romaniatv.net/a-murit-senatorul-psd-stefan-stoica-era-bolnav-de-cancer_124484.html A murit senatorul PSD Stefan] {{ro icon}}</ref><ref>[http://www.nineoclock.ro/senator-stefan-stoica-and-deputy-mircea-grosaru-died/ Senator Stefan Stoica and Deputy Mircea Grosaru died] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002163829/http://www.nineoclock.ro/senator-stefan-stoica-and-deputy-mircea-grosaru-died/ |date=2015-10-02 }}</ref>
